As a Marketing Manager
I want to identify customers interest
So that I can make a plan success launch a new product 

Scope

CRM functionality 
Customers interests report


Precondition:

CRM functionality is implemented
The Customer is registered in the online shop
The administrator is logged 

Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1: The CRM system uses customer purchase history and preferences to create targeted marketing lists
Given: The administrator is logged in 
When: Click on the " Report about customer purchase history and preferences" buttons 
Then: Get a report









 

